                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#2r">f. 2r</locus>-v: List of the feasts dedicated to the Apostles.<quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="2r">2r</locus>: ወካዕበ፡ እጽሕፍ፡ ሕልቈ፡ በዓላቲሆሙ፡ ለሐዋርያት፡…</quote>
